metadata.name: Elliot Smith - Final Performance 09/19/03
metadata.description:
This photo is from a previously unreleased collection documenting the final performance by Elliot Smith. The performance took place September 19, 2003 in Salt Lake City, Utah (USA) at the University of Utah for a music festival called Redfest.

The collection consists of 17 photos (180x180) and 4 videos (480p) that were shot from inside the media fence on a Canon PowerShot G3 by musician and visual artist, James Glines.

The remaining images will be minted over the coming weeks. If you follow @custommodel on Twitter, you can find out when the next drop will happen.
